---
import SplashLayout from "@layouts/SplashLayout.astro";
import starryLogo from "../assets/blue glitter frost logo-sm.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---
<style>
a:link {
  color: blue;
  background-color: transparent;
  text-decoration: none;
}
a:visited {
  color: pink;
  background-color: transparent;
  text-decoration: none;
}
a:hover {
  color: black;
  background-color: transparent;
  text-decoration: underline;
}
a:active {
  color: yellow;
  background-color: transparent;
  text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
<SplashLayout title="FAQs">
  <div
    class="snap-start bg-white w-screen md:min-h-screen md:flex md:items-center justify-center">
    <div
    class="items-center flex flex-col-reverse justify-start md:flex-row space-x-4 w-screen">
    <div class="mt-10 m-5 w-5/6 text-left md:w-1/2 md:ml-10 lg:ml-15">
        <div class="w-auto">
        <h1
            class="text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-8xl lx:text-4xl font-bold text-balance">
            GOT QUESTIONS?
        </h1>
        <br>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-2xl lx:text-4xl font-bold text-balance">
            FIND ANSWERS TO QUESTIONS WE ALWAYS RECEIVE.
            IF YOUR QUERY IS NOT THERE, SEND US A MESSAGE!
            <br>
            <br>
            <a href = "mailto:frost@fiskeschoolpto.org?subject=Question about Fiske Frost&body= Message">FROST@FISKESCHOOLPTO.ORG</a>
        </h3>
        </div> <!--w-auto -->
    </div> <!-- mt-10 m-5 -->
    <div class="items-center flex flex-col w-1/2 mt-16">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
        <Image
            formats={["jpg", "webp"]}
            src={starryLogo}
            alt="Save the Date"
            class="w-2/3"
        />
        </div> <!-- flex justify-center -->
    </div> <!-- items-center -->
    </div> <!-- parent items-center -->
</div> <!--snap start -->

<div
    class="snap-start bg-white w-screen md:min-h-screen md:flex md:items-center justify-center">
    <div
    class="items-center flex flex-col-reverse justify-start md:flex-row space-x-4 w-screen">
    <div class="mt-10 m-5 w-5/6 text-left md:w-1/2 md:ml-10 lg:ml-15">
        <div class="w-auto">
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>When and where is the event taking place?</b>
                <br>
                <br>
                Date: March 22, 2024
                <br>
                Time: 7 p.m. onwards
                <br>
                Venue: Cafe Escadrille, 26 Cambridge St, Burlington, MA 01803
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How much are the tickets for?</b>
                <br><br>
                $100 per person.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Are you charging Fiske teachers and staff to attend Frost?</b>
                <br><br>
                No, Fiske Frost is free for all Fiske School teachers and staff.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How can I support our Fiske teachers and staff? </b>
                <br><br>
                You can contribute to teachers' and staff's tickets during your ticket checkout. You'll find suggested donation amounts, or you can enter your own. Your support is highly valued, and we appreciate any monetary contributions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>I can't attend, but I want to donate towards Fiske staff tickets. How?</b>
                <br><br>
                You can donate to Fiske staff tickets on our website. Visit FiskeFrost or FiskePTO, and you'll find a dedicated tab for staff ticket donations. We appreciate your generosity and thoughtfulness. 
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Is there a dress code for the event?</b>
                <br><br>
                Guests are encouraged to dress in their semi-formal or cocktail attire.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Is this a sit-down dinner?</b>
                <br><br>
                Frost is an event designed to mingle and build community. The event's unique cocktail lounge setup ensures that appetizers will be served throughout the evening.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Is there a dance floor? </b>
                <br><br>
                Yes. The evening begins with soothing live acoustic music, creating an inviting atmosphere. As the night progresses, a DJ takes the stage, and a dance floor emerges, providing an opportunity to dance the night away.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Is the event family-friendly?</b>
                <br><br>
                No, this is an adult-only event.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Can I buy my drinks in advance?</b>
                <br><br>
                Yes, or you can buy them online at the time of ticket purchase and at the venue. 
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Are you serving non-alcoholic beverages?</b>
                <br><br>
                Yes. We have created a special mocktail just for you. There will be standard non-alcoholic beverages available, too. 
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Are you inclusive of dietary requirements?</b>
                <br><br>
                Our menu is carefully curated, catering to various dietary preferences.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>What parking options are available?</b>
                <br><br>
                The venue is only a 9-minute drive from Fiske School and has ample parking. 
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>What items are in the silent auction?</b>
                <br><br>
                The silent auction showcases items with a collective value of over $10,000, all
                thoughtfully curated by our dedicated planning committee into about 50 
                different packages. You will find a variety of offerings to meet all interests 
                including tickets to shows, gift cards to restaurants, passes to local 
                attractions, day trip ideas, enrichment programs and much more.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>What items are in the live auction?</b>
                <br><br>
                We will be offering 8 - 10 items to bid on during the live auction. The live 
                auction will feature special experiences and unique items. For the first time 
                we will be offering each grade the ability to bid on a “Sleep Under” at Fiske. 
                More details on each live auction item will be communicated leading up to the
                Frost.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Where can I see the items in advance?</b>
                <br><br>
                A list of auction items will be posted on the Frost website closer to the event.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How will I bid on the items that I like?</b>
                <br><br>
                <b>Silent auction: </b>You will write your bid amount and contact information on 
                the auction form. 
                <b>Live auction: </b>Get your bidding paddle upon check-in for easy bidding access.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How do I pay for my item?</b>
                <br><br>
                You can pay by cash, credit or check.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Do I get to take my item home the same night?</b>
                <br><br>
                Yes, all auction items will be available for pick up to take home that night. 
                Pick up will be from 10 - 11 PM.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How do I take part in the 50/50 Raffle?</b>
                <br><br>
                You can buy raffle tickets when you buy your event ticket online or at the 
                event itself. We offer various purchase options.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>How does the 50/50 Raffle work?</b>
                <br><br>
                The total funds collected are split equally between one lucky winner and the 
                Parent-Teacher Organization (PTO).
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg xl:text-xl mt-5">
                <b>Who do I contact for further inquiries?</b>
                <br><br>
                Please feel free to reach us at <a href = "mailto:frost@fiskeschoolpto.org?subject=Question about Fiske Frost&body= Message">frost@fiskeschoolpto.org</a>
            </p>
            </div> <!-- class wauto -->
        </div> <!-- mt-10 m-5 -->
    </div> <!-- parent items-center -->
</div> <!--snap start -->
</SplashLayout>
